text: Khatuna Narimanidze is an archer from Georgia. She was born on 2 February 1974. Narimanidze competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics, 2004 Summer Olympics, 2008 Summer Olympics, and the 2016 Summer Olympics.Khatuna Phutkaradze- NarimanidzeKhatuna NARIMANIDZE == References == Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Archers from Georgia (country) Category:Olympians for Georgia (country)
